 16→/**
 17→ * Updates the 'replies' table in the database based on the provided data.
 18→ *
 19→ * @param {Array} repliesToUpdate - An array of objects containing reply data to update.
 20→ * @returns {Promise} A promise that resolves when the updates are completed.
